  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Humanitarian Assistance to People Affected by Cholera Outbreak in Chad</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will focus on the reduction of the vulnerability of the most affected and at risk populations to current, on -going cholera outbreak through the following activities:    &#x2022; &#x2022; Disinfection / spraying of cholera affected households, including the distribution of hygiene kits and hygiene promotion sessions;  &#x2022; Hygiene awareness campaigns focused on cholera prevention, including the distribution of water purification chemicals and soap in public locations;  &#x2022;</narrative>
  </description>
